Package: pkg-inspector
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: assess how ready a project is to be packaged and distributed
 pkg-inspector analyses a project directory and produces a packaging
 readiness report. It checks for pyproject.toml, license clarity, tests,
 CI configuration, dependency pinning and declared entry points, then
 prints a weighted 0-100 score. A --min-score flag makes it usable as a
 CI gate.
